  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `v1.10.2-stable`\r\nOS & Version: Linux  ubuntu-18.04\r\nGolang version: go1.15.7\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nI got `result` equal to `0x0`.\r\n\r\n```\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0x737be7600\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0x0\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0x9502f9000\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0x0\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0xa3e9ab800\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0xa7a358200\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0xa3e9ab800\"}\r\n\r\n~/coin$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":76,\"result\":\"0x0\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nI just run the geth with docker and command like this : `geth  --syncmode full --maxpeers 100 --cache 40960 --snapshot=false --txpool.nolocals --http.api \"eth,net,web3\" --datadir.ancient /data/ancient --ws --ws.addr 0.0.0.0 --ws.port  8036 --ws.origins \"*\" --http --http.port 8136 --http.addr 0.0.0.0 --http.corsdomain \"*\" --http.vhosts \"*\"`\r\n\r\nThen, i ran `curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":76}' http://127.0.0.1:8136 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"` in another console.\r\nI ran it many times in a short period of time. \r\nResult like above.Whether or not the node have finished synchronizing blocks.",
